{"tid":1311411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將連登推介俾長輩，有冇得諗","createTime":"2019-07-13T07:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T13:22:13.000Z","uid":267881,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6395f8cb2d4d8fde528aff629b547f5b04eb5a83","tid":1311411,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:27:05.000Z","msg":"既然連儂牆都進化到貼長輩圖+反紅媒<br />\n不如叫佢地裝連登app，跟貼時事<br />\n而家連登個朵咁響，免費安裝免費資訊喎！<br />\n第一手現場消息喎！聽落都吸引<br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句，唔係要佢地全力支持我地抗爭<br />\n至少可以知道班連登仔諗緊乜搞緊乜<br />\n潛移默化下會多左用另一個角度思考<br />\n<br />\n同時間又可以破解&rdquo;年青人&rdquo;呢個標籤<br />\n好多師奶呀叔都好勇武，我地全部都要connect<br />\n種子一定要全方位大量散播<br />\n呢個方法又係極低成本唔會輸嘅<br />\n放膽向身邊長輩介紹，就算係藍絲都得<br />\n咪同佢地講班搞事份子係度組織架<br />\n深藍會頂唔順剷app，剩低班人會慢性染黃<br />\n好多巴打都話屋企人接收多左資訊冇以前咁藍<br />\n試下冇壞！"},{"pid":"dcff1b649ea84f434423f30211a53bee4b0be6f2","tid":1311411,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"又多批人帶風向"},{"pid":"bd616fc2123e9b0853c36100d4580e20e2ff6c7f","tid":1311411,"uid":265192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"開個Facebook同Yourube做比長者仲好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536b146486ae8e849f615882c9e598533d84ab82","tid":1311411,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"但係唔可以畀佢哋發言"},{"pid":"6d5b1c4b10d4cae27d12282e0946ce85b1679b12","tid":1311411,"uid":267881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd616fc2123e9b0853c36100d4580e20e2ff6c7f","tid":1311411,"uid":265192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"開個Facebook同Yourube做比長者仲好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:30:44.000Z","msg":"以我所知facebook有手足搞緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f603641e4fe5f4b1369dba429dd261ba474a00","tid":1311411,"uid":261982,"like":0,"dislike